<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.3">
<l>eṉṉuḷ kalantavaṉ ceṅkaṉivāy ceṅkamala</l>
<l>miṉṉuñ cuṭarmalaikku kaṇpātaṅ kaikamala</l>
<l>maṉṉu muḻuvē ḻulakum vayiṟṟiṉuḷa</l>
<l>taṉṉuḷ kalavāta tepporuḷun tāṉilaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the one who mingled with my soul, the flashing, glowing mountain</l>
<l>of red lotus with a red fruit mouth, [there] are eye, foot, [and] hand lotusses;</l>
<l>in [his] belly there are the whole lasting seven worlds.</l>
<l>The is no thing at all that is not mingled in him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
